<para style="q1">

<verse number="3" style="v" />My mouth will speak wisdom</para>

<para style="q1">and the meditation of my heart will be of understanding.</para>

<para style="q1">

<verse number="4" style="v" />I will incline my ear to a parable;</para>

<para style="q1">I will begin my parable with the harp.</para>

<para style="q1">

<verse number="5" style="v" />Why should I fear the days of evil,</para>

<para style="q1">when iniquity surrounds me at my heels?</para>
